::Zardus/Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Zardus walks into the lab of the Alliance base, glancing at Reptilica and 
Bloodystrike, then at the femm on the table.

"Allright, you two can go now," he says, walking toward the table and getting 
ready to reprogramm this new bot. Reptilica and Bloodystrike both  take one 
last look at her, walking out of the room.
